      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical and FDA in-house FEA codes are under formal software quality management plans compliant with 21 CFR Part 11 and ISO 9001. Version-controlled releases with documented regression test suites are required. Gradation 2 requires documented SQA plan with traceability to test cases.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R19.2 is used under a validated installation with documented SQA procedures. FDA in-house code is version-controlled under Git with automated regression tests covering linear-elastic and contact benchmark cases. SQA plan references are archived in the study record."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
