      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification requires demonstration that the solver correctly implements the governing equations via benchmark problems with known analytical solutions. Gradation 2 requires at least one published benchmark comparison for linear elasticity and contact mechanics relevant to the COU.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical has been verified against NAFEMS benchmarks LE1 and LE10 for linear elasticity and against Hertzian contact benchmarks. Results are within 1% of analytical solutions. Documentation is included in the study appendix."
